Title: Termination For Cause
Plot: Jake and the Rangers take on Goetz and Ravenwood while a Jericho Ranger makes a choice that will alter his life. Meanwhile, an old friend comes to warn Heather that her loyalties to Major Beck have placed her in serious danger.
GuestStars: Michael Rubenstone, Brad Raider, Aasif Mandvi, Link Baker, Nick Hoffa, David Meunier, Geno Monterio, Bill Tangradi, Patrick Rowe, Terrel Clayton
